Package: GLP
Title: Redefining High Variable Genes Using LOESS Regression with Positive Ratio
Version: 0.0.0.9000
Authors@R: 
    person("Yue", "Xie", email = "xieyue@genomics.cn", role = c("aut", "cre"))
Maintainer: Yue Xie <xieyue@genomics.cn>
Description: GLP is a specialized tool for feature selection that utilizes a robust 
             LOESS (locally estimated scatterplot smoothing) regression model based 
             on the relationship between gene average expression and positive ratio.
